DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN
       _v_._l_a_b_e_l makes a label-file from a GRASS vector file.  Labels  are  read
       from  text file which contains category and label on each row separated
       by space. Example of text file:
       1 Kamenice
       2 Cerna Desna
       3 Bila Desna

       In current version only lines are labeled and label  is  created  along
       line.



